To select the namespace in the kubernetes we need to install kubens - (https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx/releases)

cd /usr/local/bin
wget https://github.com/ahmetb/kubectx/releases/download/v0.9.5/kubens_v0.9.5_linux_x86_64.tar.gz
tar -xzvf kubens_v0.9.5_linux_x86_64.tar.gz

Goto Terminal type $kubens to check namespaces
To change ns type  $kubens namespace-name 
                   $kubens devops


